      "Trophy Fish locations: caught anywhere with no reqs — Blobfish, Golden Fish, Lavahorse, Mana Ray (needs 1200 mana), Slugfish (bobber in lava 20s), Sulphur Skitter (near sulphur ore), Vanille (starter lava rod, no enchantments), Obfuscated 1-3 (chained bait requirements).",
