      "Common strategies: Karate+Moldfin at the dojo/Mystic Marsh border. Volcanic Trio — stand high in the volcano near a geyser for Steaming-Hot Flounder, Volcanic Stonefish, and Flyfish at once (bonus Gusher right after an eruption). Flyfish+1 — spots beside the volcano catch flyfish and moldfin/skeleton fish together.",
